*
!*.py
!requirements.txt
!README.md
!ShapeFile.png
!su_sheet_example.png

# Rock-mask result screenshots shown in the README
!AutomatingRockMaskImages/
!AutomatingRockMaskImages/*.png

# SAM prototype: track the code, docs, and small metrics JSONs. The large
# binaries — model weights (*.pt/*.pth), geopackages/shapefiles, orthos, and
# preview PNGs — stay out of git. See ROCK_MODEL.md "Large files (not in git)"
# for where to place the weights after downloading so the code runs.
# (Un-ignore the dir first: the global `*` excludes it, and a negation can't
#  re-include a file whose parent dir is excluded.)
!SAM_prototype/
SAM_prototype/*
!SAM_prototype/*.py
!SAM_prototype/*.md
!SAM_prototype/*.json
